des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control any of your Brookstone Smart products as soon as you connect Alexa to your Brookstone Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Brookstone Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register in our "Brookstone Smart" app;
(3). Put purchased Brookstone product into pairing mode;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Brookstone Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Brookstone Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Brookstone Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Brookstone Smart", and you'll be navigated to login page;
(9). Follow the instruction on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim living room light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
